  "name": "Building Blocks - ECRR Building Blocks repository",
  "abstract": "Building blocks for EarthCube Resource Registry (ECRR) metadata profiles,\nusing the OGC Building Blocks pattern.\n",
  "description": "Modular schema components for ECRR resource type metadata. Imports shared\nschema.org property building blocks from the CDIF Building Blocks repository.\n",
  "modified": "2026-03-16T22:10:41.608342",
